VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'then here you have the low VRAMm in layer of floating options. So, these are both options that are used to use less VRAM to train the Laura. And you can either use none of them if you want like the fastest training possible. If you'

[04:31] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'have like, I don\'t know, like 16 GB of VRAM, for example, you can definitely just disable both of these options. But if you have less than 16 GB of VRAM, you definitely might want to enable this option as well as enable layer'

[04:44] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'offloading. And here what you\'re going to do is that you\'re also going to offload 0% for the transformer but 100% for the text encoder. Using this in combination with all the other'

[04:56] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'parameters will allow you to train a Laura with less than 12 GB of VRAM which is really really cool for such an amazing model. Now you can technically use even less VRAM. I\'ve seen people train it with like 8 GB of VRAM as well'

